==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: magnetic field
<hw>magnetic field</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Physics)</fld> <def>The
space around a magnet through which it exerts magnetic force; a field of
force surrounding a permanent magnet, electrical current, or a moving
charged particle; called also <altname>magnetic flux</altname> and
<altname>field of magnetic force</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>magnetic field strength</ent>⟦br⟧
